OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fbrightness and a few showers this
OL,7,Fevening.
OL,8,
OL,9,CFriday:FOrkney will see the odd shower
OL,10,Fat first otherwise dry and sunny.
OL,11,FCloudy start with showers across
OL,12,FShetland, turning dry and bright by
OL,13,Fafternoon. Windy across Orkney late
OL,14,Fevening.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,17,FShetland wet and windy on Saturday,
OL,18,FOrkney seeing rain in the morning.
OL,19,FSunny spells and occasional showers on
OL,20,FSunday and Monday. Breezy on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
